* The metalog distribution is generalization of the logistic distribution, in which power series expansions in terms of formula_42 are substituted for logistic parameters formula_3 and formula_23. The resulting metalog quantile function is highly shape flexible, has a simple closed form, and can be fit to data with linear least squares.

